{"id": "art-2151", "label": "Art. 2151", "title": "Art. 2151: Durata controlului judiciar", "slug": "art-2151", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_950275714\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2215\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_950275714\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 215<sup>1</sup>:\nDurata controlului judiciar </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1746161462\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2214\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1746161462\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În cursul urm&#259;ririi penale, m&#259;sura controlului\njudiciar se poate dispune de c&#259;tre procuror sau de c&#259;tre\njudec&#259;torul de drepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i pe o durat&#259; de\ncel mult 60 de zile.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_735773672\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2213\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_735773672\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În cursul urm&#259;ririi penale, controlul judiciar\npoate fi prelungit de c&#259;tre procuror, prin ordonan&#355;&#259;, dac&#259;\nse men&#355;in temeiurile care au determinat luarea m&#259;surii sau au\nap&#259;rut temeiuri noi care s&#259; justifice prelungirea acestuia, fiecare\nprelungire neputând s&#259; dep&#259;&#351;easc&#259; 60 de zile. Prevederile\nart. 212 alin. (1) &#351;i (3) se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2046175090\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2212\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2046175090\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Dispozi&#355;iile alin. (2) sunt aplicabile &#351;i în\ncazul în care m&#259;sura a fost luat&#259; de c&#259;tre judec&#259;torul de\ndrepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1286899222\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2211\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1286899222\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Ordonan&#355;a procurorului prin care, în\ncondi&#355;iile alin. (2) sau (3), s-a prelungit m&#259;sura controlului\njudiciar se comunic&#259; în aceea&#351;i zi inculpatului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_441891825\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2210\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_441891825\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Împotriva ordonan&#355;ei procurorului prin care, în\ncondi&#355;iile prev&#259;zute la alin. (2) &#351;i (3), s-a prelungit\nm&#259;sura controlului judiciar, inculpatul poate face plângere la\njudec&#259;torul de drepturi &#351;i libert&#259;&#355;i de la instan&#355;a\nc&#259;reia i-ar reveni competen&#355;a s&#259; judece cauza în fond,\ndispozi&#355;iile art. 213 aplicându-se în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1000718809\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2209\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1000718809\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)În cursul urm&#259;ririi penale, durata m&#259;surii\ncontrolului judiciar nu poate s&#259; dep&#259;&#351;easc&#259; un an,\ndac&#259; pedeapsa prev&#259;zut&#259; de lege este amenda sau închisoarea de\ncel mult 5 ani, respectiv 2 ani, dac&#259; pedeapsa prev&#259;zut&#259; de lege\neste deten&#355;iunea pe via&#355;&#259; sau închisoarea mai mare de 5 ani.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2041864806\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2208\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2041864806\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Judec&#259;torul de camer&#259; preliminar&#259;, în\nprocedura de camer&#259; preliminar&#259;, sau instan&#355;a, în cursul\njudec&#259;&#355;ii, poate dispune luarea m&#259;surii controlului judiciar\nfa&#355;&#259; de inculpat pe o durat&#259; ce nu poate dep&#259;&#351;i 60 de\nzile.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1550882194\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2207\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1550882194\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)În cursul judec&#259;&#355;ii, durata total&#259; a\ncontrolului judiciar nu poate dep&#259;&#351;i un termen rezonabil &#351;i, în\nnicio situa&#355;ie, nu poate dep&#259;&#351;i 5 ani de la momentul trimiterii\nîn judecat&#259;.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_997020412\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2206\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_997020412\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)La expirarea termenelor prev&#259;zute la alin. (8),\ninstan&#355;a de judecat&#259; poate dispune luarea unei alte m&#259;suri\npreventive, în condi&#355;iile legii.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>SEC&#354;IUNEA 4:Controlul judiciar pe\ncau&#355;iune</span></b></p>"}